---
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">// ABOUT NAMEGATA</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">行方市について</h2>
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="card info-card">
        <h3 class="info-heading">地理</h3>
        <p class="info-text">
          茨城県南東部に位置し、西に霞ヶ浦、東に北浦。
          二つの湖に挟まれた豊かな水郷地帯。
        </p>
        <div class="info-stats">
          <div class="info-stat">
            <span class="info-stat-value text-blue">222.48</span>
            <span class="info-stat-label">km² 面積</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-stat">
            <span class="info-stat-value text-green">~32,000</span>
            <span class="info-stat-label">人口（推計）</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card info-card">
        <h3 class="info-heading">市章</h3>
        <p class="info-text">
          3つの帆を模した「N」のデザイン。
          麻生町・北浦町・玉造町の合併（2005年）を象徴。
        </p>
        <div class="info-colors">
          <div class="color-chip">
            <span class="color-dot" style="background: #3b82f6"></span>
            <span>青 — 霞ヶ浦・北浦</span>
          </div>
          <div class="color-chip">
            <span class="color-dot" style="background: #22c55e"></span>
            <span>緑 — 豊かな自然</span>
          </div>
          <div class="color-chip">
            <span class="color-dot" style="background: #f97316"></span>
            <span>赤 — 太陽</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card info-card">
        <h3 class="info-heading">シンボル</h3>
        <div class="symbols">
          <div class="symbol-row">
            <span class="symbol-icon">🌸</span>
            <div>
              <span class="symbol-label">市の花</span>
              <span class="symbol-value">コスモス</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="symbol-row">
            <span class="symbol-icon">🌲</span>
            <div>
              <span class="symbol-label">市の木</span>
              <span class="symbol-value">ケヤキ</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="symbol-row">
            <span class="symbol-icon">🐦</span>
            <div>
              <span class="symbol-label">市の鳥</span>
              <span class="symbol-value">ヨシキリ</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(300px, 100%), 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .info-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .info-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .info-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .info-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .info-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .info-stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .info-stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  .info-colors {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .color-chip {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .color-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .symbols {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .symbol-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .symbol-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .symbol-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    display: block;
  }

  .symbol-value {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
